    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home! This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just left the showroom. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it\u2019s always sparkling. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready for its next adventure, you\u2019ve found it! It drives like a dream and is ready to hit the road today. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
