    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade specimen that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior retains its deep, factory-original luster with zero imperfections, stone chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the leather is supple with no bolster wear, and the buttons still retain their crisp, tactile feedback. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive binder of every service interval performed by certified technicians. Every seal is dry, the undercarriage is immaculate, and it drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually new example of this model. VIN and full history report available upon request for serious inquiries.",
